events.name: Foxtail Farm to The Old Forest

parameters: Better not leave yet. I've still got work to do.
Player hasn't visited from the overworld
There might come a time when you'll have to use this thing,
and not just for chopping wood. I've been out here for a
couple of hours and I've already seen a few \C[13]Triffids\C
lurking around the perimeter in the woods.
They seem to be encroaching more and more lately...they
used to not even bother. You understand, son? You do what you
have to do to protect the farm.
Now Chestnut has been acting up a little bit. Why don't you
go in the barn and check if everything's ok.
Did you check the barn yet?
Did you check the barn yet?
Huh...well as I said, something strange is going on. You
And one more word of advice...if you encounter a monster in the
wild, you can always try to run away. Just \C[3]double tap\C while
in battle to bring up the menu option.
And that's all you need to know! The prologue isn't
really complete yet, so you're free to go off the
farm and wander to your heart's desire. See ya later.
Remember, we are always here for you son.
